lyrics:
1. Nga kinsanhusa nga ndhi ni yesu bwemba ngandhi mu makono ge;
Mpulira emiraala n’obulamu bembanga ndi mumakonoge.

Refrain:
Banga, banga, munhwevu mu makono ge;
Banga munhwevu, banga munhwevu, banga munhweve mumakono ge.
Banga, banga, mumakon’agatalivagho.
Banga munhwevu, banga munhwevu, mu makono agatalivagho.

2. Kiba kikalamu okutambula bwembangandhi mumakono ge;
Kasana kaaka yenja mbonayo bwemba ngandhi mumakono ge.

3. Kiki kyentya nze ki ekinzindula bwembanga ndhi mumakono ge;
Bwemba ni yesu mba nemiraala bwemba ngandhi mumakono ge.

1. Yesu yakakasa atighange yamp(a) ekitiisa eyomwigulu;
Omusik’oghobulokozi nazaalibw’omwoy’omwamufu.

Refrain:
Leka nze nhemb(e) olwekyafayo,
kamusaakenga buli sagha;
Leka nze nhemb(e) olwekyafayo,
Nga nsaaka Yesu oyo bulidho.

2. Mulimo gwange kumusaka eisahnu lyange kumusaaka nga;
Bamalayika be bwebaidha bandag’ omukwano gwa Yesu.

3. Ebyange byonabyona byaagha nze bwenamwikiriza yabimpa;
Ndighano nteega bweningayo ndhidhwire isanhu lyokwendakwe.

1. Inhulula’bantu fayo kabafa, baghaluze okuva mukufa;
Dhuna ab(o) abagwa beedha abagwire bakobere yesu alokola.

Refrain:
Inhulula (a)bantu fayo kubafa
Yesu ghakis’ate alokola

2. Ghaire nga banhooma, yesu abateeze abaghonie babe abaanabe;
Yogera kukugonza kwe nekisa, Bwebaikiriza idhaku baghonia.

3. (O)mulimu munene gwend(a) abakozi, abeghayo bakole namaani;
Baire mungir’enton(o) enabatuusa eri yesu eyafa kulwaife.

1. Kol’ obwire bughayo, ghuna munky’okole;
Ni mu musulo mwona, kola bukole;
Akasana ngakaka, nenduba bweb’egwa;
Ekiseera kiriidha, nga tosobola.

2. Kol’obwire bughayo, (O)kubita muntuyo;
Sagha ngadhikaliyo, mulimo gughe;
Ekisera kiriidha, mwolikungulira;
Mwoliletera kwebyo, byeghakungula;

3. Kol’obwire bughayo, mubimpombye kola;
Muka-nzimye nzimw(e) omwo kolabukole
Bwire nga buzibyeinho munzikiza enene.
Kisera kirituuka olighangula.

1. Fugha endek(a) omukumi, labula kiisi muntu;
Kiisi agighulir’oyo, yenenye akirize.

Refrain:
Omukumi omwesigw(a) einho, gifuyire ghaigulu;
Obukwenda bughulirwe, (a) basibe balokoke.

2. Gifuyire kugasozi, nimugabira mwona;
Mulukoola nagayandha, gifuyire ghaigulu.

3. Kubigulumo byengudo, nikumatagho kwona;
Bakob’ekisera nekyo Yesu ateze mwngughe.

4. Noyo azitoghereirwa ngayenda aghumule,
Yesu akweghembye idha mangu ofun’ekghumulo.

1. Twanhirize Sabbato: Eyagheebwa abantu;
Okuwumuliraku: Luleet(a) Ekitangaala.

2. Kiwumulo Ky’eidembe: Eritughebwa Yesu;
Kitoolagho entiisa: Ekituutusa eka.

3. (O)lunaku Olwamufu: Olwo’kusaaka Yesu;
Olutugezighaza: Tufun(a) Obwibuka bwe.

4. Twanhirize sabbato: Olwidhwiir(e) Obwamufu;
Ganha Lube Lwa nkabi: Mumwoyo gwange Yesu.

1. Tugh(e) Okugonza Buliidho, (o)tuzuusenga Bukalamu;
(O)tubisenga Mundhikiiza, Twidhuzenga Amaani go.

2. Tughenga Ekivunika, Obe Nhiife Mukusaba;
Sonhigha ebibi byaife, Tugh(e) Ebidhuubo Byo Yesu.

3. Ife nga tulikukola, Myoyo Gyaife Gikusaake;
Tuve Kubukomb(e) obwensi, kub(a) otugha Kiisi Kintu.

4. Leka byetukola Leero, Bibe Byankabi Musengwa;
Leka Bibenga Mukwampa, Ogutwiiza Kumpi Niighe.

5. Niighe wenka Atugonza, Tutukuze Tutuuk(e) eyo;
Otuyambenga Buliidho, Tube Ng(a) Okusaba Kwaife.

1. N’ekivunika Yesu ayeta, Ighe nhinze tuj(e) eka;
Ali agho kumulyango ayemereire; Ng(a) alinda Ighe nhinze.

Refrain:
Mwiidhe, mwiidhe eka; Imw(e) abakooghu mwiidhe;
Yesu ayeta n’ekivunika kye; Omwonoon(i) ira eka.

2. Lwaki tulwagho nga Yesu ayeta; Nga atugholereza?
(E)kisera kye kivunika kighayo; Kyatugha ife leero?

3. (E)kiseera ky’omusango kituuse; Tulumuke ekibi;
Edhikiiza n’okufa nga biseese; Okumalagh(o) abantu.

4. Dhuuba okugonza kw(e) okukologho; Kwasubiz(a) abantu be;
Ghaira nga twayonoona asonigha; Ighe nhinze tubeegho.

1. Kiisi aghulira aje akobe enjiri egema ku-mulo-kozi;
Buli gwo yagana ighe mukobere ajikiriza ng’aidha.

Refrain:
Ajighulira najikiriza alangirire kunsozi nebyalo,
Nti Yesu alikweta eyabula ir’eka; akwikiriza ng’aidha.

2. Kiisi abangaidha atalwayo ng(a) olwigi lukaali kwigulibwagho;
Yesu namazima er’engira yaife, buli asobola idhe.

3. Oy(o) ab(a) aghulire (e)kisubizo aguma yanhwera olwekisubizo;
Aleni banange mwi-kirize kyabazinga Yesu aidha.

1. Naghab(a) okuva kuyesu buti ndhidh’eka;
Ebibi bingi byenkoze musengwa ndhidha eka.

Refrain:
Ndhidh(a) eka ndhidh’eka obutairayo
Ngema mumikonogyo musengwa ndhidha

2. Nze ndwiregho nganhonona buti ndhidhe’eka;
Mumaziga kanenhenie musengwa ndhidha.

3. Nkoye ekibi nokwengengeta buti ndhidh’eka;
Nesiga ng(a) ekigambo kyo Musengwa ndhidha.

4. Nighe ghenk’eisubi lyange buti ndhidh(a) eka;
Kuba ghafa ng’onfirira musengwa ndhdha.

5. Musayi gwo nogunaaza buti ndhidh’eka;
Gunaaza naba mweru inho musengwa ndhidha.

1. Mpulir(a) erobozi ngalinkobera nti;
Oli munafu inho ghenhweze mukusaba.

Refrain:
Yabisasula ebya mandhwanga,
Yanaazaku ebyangubya nab(a) oti muzira.

2. Yesu nze kyenzwire musayi gwo gwonka;
Gughanga okunaaza nafuuk(a) omugonvu einho.

3. Nze nziira kalungi kampees’ekisakyo;
Buyinza bwo yesu nobump’obulam.

4. Nze bwendyemerera mumaiso gekyambi;
Nga mpangwire ensi ndyekaz’eyanfirira.

1. Musengwa Yasubiz(a) Abantu be;
Bona Ndidha Mangu Nbatwaale Eka”
Mwekalangule (O)lwekisubizo;
Muteegererenga; Timughongera

Mwekalangule; “Ekisuubiizo;
(O)bwa Kyabazinga Buli Bagheebwa
Era Mwikaale Ku Kyambi Kyange
Mbatiikir(e) Engule; mwekalangule”

2. Leka Tumoge Ng(a) Era Tusaba; Ezir(a)
Alimanha Saagha Yaliidha
Twiidh(i) Ali Kwiidh(a) Ay(e) Olunaku
Kamaal(a) Ebiraga—Luli Kump(i) Inho

3. Ekibono Kye N’esuubi Lyaife;
Yes(u) Aliboneka Mu Kitiisa Kye
Ekisuubiz(o) EKighul(a) Ebindi;
“Bona Ndidha Mangu, mwekalangule”

1. Tukola ife neisanhu lwakuba ng’atwenda.
Okwenda kwe kutufuula kufayo kubandi.
Ife abato Yesu oyo atwenda inho;
Bwatwenda tumufanane.
Tufeyo nga kubandi tubenga bakisa,
Lwo mukwano gwa Yesu oyo tubenga nekisa.

2. Ensi eno eidhwiire enaku kulwala n’okufa;
Lw’omutimo omusasizi tukole byayenda.

3. Bwetulyetebwa eka tulighon’ ensieno;
Tulibanga twemba enhembo edhisaaka Yesu.

1. Nooni(a) Obumanhiso Ng(a) otambula;
Kalala kalala nga bubita
Mubwakyabazinga bul(e) obuna;
Tuligha leero? Ighe bunoonie

Refrain:
Nooni(a) obumanhi--so; obw’obulanzi;
Obw’obwakyabazinga obuna
Noonia obumanhi--so; obw’obulanzi; tubona ekyambi

2. Obwa Assiria nobwasooka;
Obw’abamedi ni Perusia
Abagureki bafuga ensi;
N’obw(o) obwe Roma, tuligha leero?

3. (E)bigere eby’ekyuuma n’eitosi;
Binatera okumanhiangulwa
K(i) Ekinairaku nga kya kitiisa?
Kwiira kwa Yesu n’obutaghaagho

1. Kankobe Yes(u) Okulebwa kwange;
Tighanga Kubibeedha Zenka
Mubughafu Bwang(e) Oyo Anamba;
Atugonza Era Afaayo

Refrain:
Kankobe Yesu! Kankobe Yesu!;
Tighanga Kubibeedha Zenka
Kankobe Yesu! Kankobe Yesu!;
Yenka N’aghanga Okunamba

2. Kankobe Yes(u) Ebindhugumiza;
N’omugonzi Ghaif(e) Ogh’ekisa
Bwemukoba Aghang(a) Okundhuna;
Yatoolagh(o) Ebindhugumiza

3. (E)byensi Binzimayiza Mu Kibi;
Ndebebwa Mu Mwooy(o) Okwonoona
Kankobe Yesu, Oyo Anamba;
Alimp(a) Obuwangunzi Bw’ensi.
